---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Specialist Treatments | Medical Care and Rehabilitation"
  description="Comprehensive guide to specialist treatments available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about advanced medical care for service-related injuries and conditions.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Specialist Treatments for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) provides access to a wide range of specialist treatments for veterans with service-related injuries or conditions. This page offers a comprehensive overview of the various specialist treatments available and how to access them.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Advanced Pain Management</h2>
        <p>For veterans dealing with chronic pain, we offer:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Multidisciplinary pain management programmes</li>
          <li>Advanced medication therapies, including targeted drug delivery systems</li>
          <li>Nerve block procedures and radiofrequency ablation</li>
          <li>Spinal cord stimulation and peripheral nerve stimulation</li>
          <li>Cognitive behavioural therapy for pain management</li>
          <li>Biofeedback and mindfulness-based stress reduction techniques</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Neurological Rehabilitation</h2>
        <p>Specialised care for brain and spinal injuries includes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive cognitive rehabilitation therapy</li>
          <li>Neurofeedback and brain-computer interface treatments</li>
          <li>Advanced mobility therapies using robotic assistance</li>
          <li>Virtual reality-based rehabilitation programmes</li>
          <li>Neuroplasticity-focused treatments</li>
          <li>Specialised therapies for traumatic brain injuries and spinal cord injuries</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Prosthetics and Orthotics</h2>
        <p>State-of-the-art prosthetic and orthotic services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom-designed, 3D-printed prosthetic limbs</li>
          <li>Microprocessor-controlled joints for enhanced mobility</li>
          <li>Osseointegration procedures for direct skeletal attachment of prostheses</li>
          <li>Advanced orthotics for spinal and limb support</li>
          <li>Bionic limb technologies with sensory feedback capabilities</li>
          <li>Specialised prosthetics for sports and high-impact activities</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Regenerative Medicine</h2>
        <p>Cutting-edge treatments to promote healing:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Stem cell therapies for tissue regeneration</li>
          <li>Platelet-rich plasma injections for joint and soft tissue injuries</li>
          <li>Bioengineered tissue grafts for complex wound healing</li>
          <li>Gene therapy approaches for genetic and acquired disorders</li>
          <li>Exosome therapy for cellular regeneration</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Advanced Surgical Procedures</h2>
        <p>Access to cutting-edge surgical interventions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Minimally invasive and robotic-assisted surgeries</li>
          <li>Advanced reconstructive procedures, including microsurgery techniques</li>
          <li>Targeted muscle reinnervation for improved prosthetic control</li>
          <li>Regenerative surgical techniques for joint preservation</li>
          <li>Innovative spinal surgeries, including artificial disc replacement</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Specialised Mental Health Treatments</h2>
        <p>Advanced therapies for mental health conditions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>EMDR (Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing) therapy for PTSD</li>
          <li>Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation (TMS) for depression</li>
          <li>Virtual reality exposure therapy for anxiety disorders</li>
          <li>Neurofeedback for ADHD and other cognitive disorders</li>
          <li>Ketamine-assisted psychotherapy for treatment-resistant conditions</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Accessing Specialist Treatments</h2>
        <p>To access these specialist treatments:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Consult with your AFCS-assigned medical professional for a referral</li>
          <li>Undergo comprehensive assessments to determine suitable treatments</li>
          <li>Receive referrals to specialist clinics or centres of excellence</li>
          <li>Participate in treatment planning and goal-setting with your care team</li>
          <li>Access to case managers to coordinate complex care needs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/medical/rehabilitation" class="text-decoration-none">Rehabilitation Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/mental-health-care" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Care</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/long-term-care" class="text-decoration-none">Long-term Care</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Treatment Consultation</h3>
            <p>Speak with a specialist to discuss treatment options tailored to your needs.</p>
            <a href="/treatment-consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Book Consultation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Treatment Centres</h3>
            <p>Find specialist treatment centres near you.</p>
            <a href="/treatment-centres" class="btn btn-secondary">Locate Centres</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
